Thus we see that \(E_{A\mid\tilde{A}}[A^{T}A]=E_{A\mid\tilde{A}}[A]\) is a diagonal matrix whose entries are \(1\) wherever \(\tilde{A}_{ii}=1\) and \(q\) wherever \(\tilde{A}_{ii}=0\). This is clearly of full rank since \(q>0\). 

